Description: UNIQUE FEATURESAWARDS - Now without alcohol, Guinness 0.0 is the iconic, best-selling stout beer, with groundbreaking innovation right at its ruby-red heart." INGREDIENTS - Guinness 0.0 revolutionary, nitrogenating widget delivers the rich smooth head and the sweetness of the malt perfectly balanced with the bitterness of the hops. At home. Every time." SERVE - Just chill. Open. Pour at 45 degrees. Enjoy!" TASTING NOTES - Smoothly balanced with bitter, sweet and roasted notes. Hints of coffee and chocolate aromas." OCCASION - Perfect with food. Or without. Guinness 0.0 is an ideal accompaniment to good friends and good times." HERITAGE - 264 years of Guinness history in every smooth, satisfying drop. SUSTAINABILITY - At Guinness we will never settle in our pursuit of a better, more sustainable future for all. Thats why, were proud to be partnering with Irish farmers undertaking the most ambitious regenerative farming project in Ireland, an approach that works in harmony with the natural environment. Search Guinness Regenerative Farming to learn more. Introducing Guinness 0.0. Brewed with our new cold filtration process This ensures you get the same beautifully smooth taste, perfectly balanced flavour and unique dark colour of Guinness Draught, just without the alcohol. The latest in 264 years of innovation, Guinness 0.0 is specially brewed to retain the characteristic flavours which make Guinness Draught our most popular beer The brewing process starts just as it always has, but with Guinness 0.0 the alcohol is gently removed through a cold filtration method. This helps to preserve its natural flavour, ensuring that the all important sweetness of the malt, the bitterness of the hops and the unique Guinness Roasted Barley flavours are all perfectly balanced. Serving Suggestion - Just chill. Open. Pour at 45 degrees. Enjoy!. Guinness 0.0 is best served chilled (between 3-5C) Tasting Notes - Just like Guinness, Guinness 0.0 is dark ruby red with a creamy head, with hints of chocolate and coffee, and is smoothly balanced with bitter, sweet, roasted notes

Blending a fragrance free formula with the benefits of dermachromatic colour technology, skin-centric active vitamin C to help brighten, and chamomile to help soothe, technocolor magenta self tanning face serum is perfect for olive-deep skin tones looking to achieve a rich, deep toned face tan. Featuring high-level tanning active ingredients, warm-toned bronzed colour enhancers and electrolyte hydration, technocolor magenta face counteracts the development of cool tones to provide the most natural result. Additional blemish control complex helps prevent breakouts and blemishes from appearing, leaving you with an enhanced, skin-blurring finish after every application." Technocolor magenta self tanning face serum perfectly blends high-level active ingredients, electrolyte hydration and magenta colour enhancers to produce the most optimal results for those with an olive to deep complexion. With every application, olive to deep skin tones will experience increased tone longevity and natural results that best enhance skin, not change it. Who is the product suitable for?"Why is technocolor magenta best suited for olive to deep skin tones? Technocolor was created through extensive research, specifically our laser skin analysis technology that examined varying skin tones and their ability to process self tanning actives which would determine their best outcome. From these findings, we discovered that those with olive to deep skin tones have a higher melanin level and are able to achieve their most optimal results through high-level tanning actives and a magenta hue, as anything olive or emerald based would produce an unnatural cool tone. Want to learn more? Visit our research development page to learn more about this cutting- edge technology and take our technocolor shade finder quiz to find your perfect shade.

Description: EFFECTIVE HYDRATION E45s Daily Cream offers effective, everyday hydration. As skin gets drier, it feels and looks less healthy and becomes less effective at retaining moisture, which leaves it even more dry. Our cream soothes, protects, and restores very dry skin it intensely replenishes moisture to sooth dryness and smooth out rough skin. The cream locks in moisture to help better protect the skin against moisture loss, and to help restore and maintain the skins moisture level. MOISTURISING INGREDIENTS Our Daily Cream contains light liquid paraffin that has emollient moisturising properties to help keep the skin hydrated. The perfume-free gentle formula is non-greasy and quickly absorbed and is even suitable for sensitive skin. The cream is easy to apply to skin and can be used whenever the skin feels dry, locking in moisture and leaving you with long-lasting softness in just 2 weeks. DERMATOLOGICALLY TESTED E45s formulation is dermatologically tested and does not contain any unnecessary colour or fragrances. It is suitable for everyday use on dry and sensitive skin for the whole family, including infants over the age of 1 month. You can apply the cream all over the body, including the face, for soft and supple skin. The cream has a low viscosity with watery consistency which can be thoroughly applied on the skin and is easily absorbed. QUALITY SKINCARE EVERY DAY For 70 years, E45 has been a skincare expert in dry and itchy skin and treatment for eczema, psoriasis, ichthyosis and other dry skin conditions. We understand the importance of quality everyday products that care for your skin with minimal fuss. The E45 range of products has been developed for different skin types and parts of the body and works hard to protect and maintain skin health. It has proven dermatological expertise dedicated to vulnerable dry skin. E45 Cream has been clinically proven to treat and soothe dry, flaking, chapped skin, as well as sunburn and detergent hands. E45 Cream's non-greasy emollient formulation leaves skin soft, comfortable and relieved. E45 Cream is also developed for more serious dry skin conditions such as eczema, dermatitis, ichthyosis and certain dry cases of psoriasis. Perfume free dermatologically tested. E45 Cream can be used as a body cream, a face cream and a hand cream. Quality skincare every day We understand the importance of quality everyday products that care for skin with minimal fuss. For 70 years, E45 has been a skincare expert in dry and itchy skin and treatment for eczema, psoriasis, ichthyosis and other dry skin conditions. It has proven dermatological expertise thats dedicated to vulnerable dry skin. The E45 range of skincare products has been developed for different skin types and different parts of the body. It works hard to protect and maintain skin health, while E45 Cream and E45 Itch Relief Cream can also improve dry skin health at every application. The voice of experience In 1952 we released our first product E45 cream. It was created by a Boots chemist in response to a customer request for a product that would soothe and protect the skin. In 1963 physicians noticed E45 cream was a beneficial treatment for dry skin conditions. At this time, we only promoted our products to hospital sales departments. It wasnt until 1980 that E45 cream was introduced to the pharmacy and retail establishments, where it was recognised for its efficacy in the treatment of dry skin. In the 1990s we extended our product range to include a complete skincare emollient therapy. Weve continued to create products with patients and their skin in mind. We strive to continue to serve the needs of both patients and healthcare professionals and produce better treatment options for patients skincare routines.

An exceptionally pure-tasting, smooth spirit with a clean palate, and the primary choice for a range of popular drinks. With countless years of heritage and unmatched quality, it is sold in over 130 countries. Founded in 1864, it gets triple distilled from a blend of different grains and filtered ten times through seven columns of environmentally sustainable charcoal for an exceptionally pure-tasting, smooth finish. Smirnoff No. 21 also makes a perfect aperitif such as the Espresso Martini - simply add 35ml Smirnoff, 25ml Espresso, 25ml coffee liquor, sugar syrup and cubed ice to a shaker and mix. Or if you prefer something more summery and refreshing, try 25 ml of Smirnoff, the citrus fruit juice of your choice, soda water, ice cubes in a highball glass and garnish with citrus fruit wedges. Smirnoff is ideal for making delicious drinks at home. As such a pure and versatile liquid, it is ideal for you to experiment and create your own cocktails. There is vodka, then theres Smirnoff. Created in 1864, Smirnoff No. 21 Premium Vodka is now the number one best-selling premium vodka brand in the world, sold in over 130 countries. The most awarded vodka brand over the past decade Won Gold in the 2019 San Francisco World Spirits Competition.

Description: ABOUT - Created in London by Scotsman Alexander Gordon in 1769, Gordon's London Dry Gin is known and loved worldwide. This classic award-winning gin has earned its reputation as 'the ginniest of gins'. TASTING NOTES - Handpicked wild juniper berries, coriander, angelica and liquorice are blended together to create Gordons London Dry Gin. HOW TO ENJOY - Best served with premium tonic water and ice for an iconic GT. It can also be used as a base for classic gin cocktails like a Bramble and a Negroni. AWARDS - Gordon's London Dry Gin is a multi-award winning spirit that is famous for its distinctive juniper character. PERFECT FOR GIFTING - The ideal gift for gin connoisseurs and those who enjoy a refreshing GT or gin-based cocktail. Gordons London Dry is a multi-award-winning gin with a distinctive juniper character. Its classic style makes it the perfect gin for the definitive GT. Mixed best with tonic over ice, garnished with lime, and enjoyed with friends. A blend of subtle juniper and botanical flavours. Handpicked wild juniper berries, coriander, angelica and liquorice are blended and triple-distilled in a secret process Gordons classic style makes it the perfect gin for the definitive GT. Best enjoyed with friends. Award-winning Gordons London Dry Gin is the worlds No.1 gin. Established in 1769 by Alexander Gordon, the Gordons distillery was founded to produce a gloriously tasting gin worthy of carrying the Gordon family name. Gordon believed that success lay in the elegant combination of pure distilled grain spirit and rich botanicals. To this day, Gordons London Dry Gin is made to the same exacting standards, with a triple-distilled guarantee for the purity of the gin. The exact blend of botanicals remains a closely guarded secret with a combination of handpicked wild juniper berries, coriander, angelica and liquorice. To savour the taste for yourself, mix a gin and tonic and garnish it with lime. Ideal at any time. Over 250 years ago, Alexander Gordon started his distillery in London and set about creating the recipe for a brilliant tasting gin. To this day Gordon's is distilled to this same exacting standard and is the worlds number one bestselling gin. Gordon's high quality and distinctive juniper flavour has come to define the taste of the classic GT.
Title: Gordon's London Dry Gin 1L

Description: Harness the power of the volcano with Volvic natural mineral water:Naturally filtered through six layers of volcanic rockUnique mineral contentSourced from a nature reserve in EuropeRecyclable bottle Starting as drops of rain falling over a mountainous landscape, Volvic mineral water stems from a nature reserve in Europe Filtered over five years through six layers of volcanic rock, our mineral water originates from deep underground, where its fully protected from pollution and untouched from source to bottle The result? A water with a unique mineral content and a crisp refreshing taste. Easy to carry and perfect for staying hydrated on-the-go, our 500ml bottles are recyclable and bottled in a renewably powered site. More from Volvic Volvic natural mineral water comes in a variety of different bottle sizes and formats. From small and compact, to larger bottles and water multipacks, theres a Volvic natural mineral water to suit you, with a taste youll love. Theres also Volvic Touch of Fruit flavoured water for when youre wanting a delicious flavour hit! Drinking at least 2 litres of fluid, including water, a day can contribute to the maintenance of normal physical and cognitive function. Consume as part of a healthy lifestyle and balanced diet. Protecting and preserving the natural mineral water resource is at the heart of Volvics DNA. Volvic actively maintains the balance of biodiversity within the area and this is reflected in our actions in helping to preserve Volvics water source by investing in local projects. Being certified B Corp since 2020, it has been written into our mission statement that as an organisation, were making a positive impact on the world around us. In addition to protecting and preserving the source, Volvic has been taking concrete steps to improve how we do business like reducing our carbon footprint. Since 1992, we have been using recyclable bottles. Throughout the years, we have significantly reduced the weight of our packaging, and increased the use of recycled plastic in our bottles with a goal of reaching 100 recycled plastic bottles by 2025. Volvic has also reduced its energy consumption by 29 since 2007 through investments in energy-efficient equipment and a circular approach to energy usage. In addition, Volvic is promoting low impact transport by having 33 of our transport in Europe by train. These initiatives collectively demonstrate a commitment to environmental sustainability, encompassing biodiversity protection, recycled and recyclable packaging, energy efficiency, renewable energy use, and low-impact transportation. Discover more about our nature protection projects at: www.volvic.co.ukvolcanic-waternature-protection. Excludes caps and labels More info: volvic.co.uk As a B-Corp we aspire to use our business as a force for good. We have been protecting the uniquely rich biodiversity of the Volvic source for more than 15 years. Certified B Corporation Mobius Loop

Description: - LIMITED EDITION GIN: A new limited release gin for artists, the curious, and free-spirited souls almost everywhere! Grand Cabaret is a decadent gin, imbued with exuberance, granting the lucky drinker a moment of almost unprecedented sensory delight!- DECADENTLY REFRESHING: Hendrick's Grand Cabaret is an indulgent creation infused with decadent STONE FRUIT FLAVOURS EXQUISITE, SWEET HERBS. Here is a sensuous cabaret of flavour pirouetting in flamboyantly light fruity freshness. - Our Master Distiller was captivated by a 17th-century experimental French recipe which celebrated the stone fruit, a sumptuous concoction that was a darling of Parisian parties. This is her marvellous modern take on this mystical masterpiece. - A DELIGHTFULLY UNUSUAL GIN FOR ALL OCCASIONS: Now you may elevate your most exclusive gatherings with the elegant sensory feast that is Hendricks GRAND CABARET. - ALLURINGLY FRUITY: Just add tonic a garnish of cucumber. Thats all. Then sit back and indulge in the unconventional allure of this handcrafted gin, celebrating a taste that adds a flamboyant dash of ooh l l to your most glorious gatherings. Introducing the NEW, LIMITED RELEASE, Hendricks Grand Cabaret gin: an indulgent creation infused with a sensuous cabaret of decadent stone fruit flavours and shimmies of sweet aromatic herbs. Inspired by a 17th-century fruity French experiment, where distilling mounds of stone fruit unexpectedly yielded a truly tasty potion sparked the imagination of our master distiller, Lesley Gracie to experiment with that same sense of poetic extravagance. At the heart of this extraordinary creation lies an unusual gin experience, drawing inspiration from the past and redefining the boundaries of traditional gin. Presented in a gorgeous 70 cl bottle, Hendricks Grand Cabaret embraces the essence of rich fruit tones and aromatic herbs, meticulously distilled to perfection, resulting in an unforgettable infused gin that delights the senses. Designed for the discerning gin lover, this premium gin will seduce your taste buds with pirouettes of decadent stone fruit and shimmies of sweet herb. The result is a decadently delicious expression of Hendricks thats ideal to add a refreshing elegance to glorious get-togethers. From a lavish soiree to an intimate gathering, Hendricks Grand Cabaret elevates your spirits collection with its captivating blend of botanicals and refreshing, fruity gin taste profile. Just add tonic a garnish of cucumber to indulge in the unconventional allure of this handcrafted gin, celebrating individuality and a taste that stands apart from the crowd. Join the grand celebration of flavour, raise your glass to the decadent beauty of Hendricks Grand Cabaret, and let your senses embark on an enchanting journey through the world of premium gin. Bottle pack size - Diameter (mm) 93 Bottle pack size - Width (mm) 180 Bottle pack size - Height (mm) 93 William Grant Sons, Ltd. is an independent family-owned distiller headquartered in the United Kingdom and founded by William Grant in 1887. Today, the luxury spirits company is run by the fifth generation of his family and distils some of the world's leading brands of Scotch whisky, including the world's favourite single malt Glenfiddich, The Balvenie range of handcrafted single malts and the world's third largest blended Scotch Grant's as well as other iconic spirits brands such as Hendrick's Gin, Sailor Jerry, Tullamore D.E.W Irish Whiskey, Monkey Shoulder and Drambuie.

Description: ABOUT - Gordon's Sicilian Lemon Distilled Gin is made with high quality ingredients and only natural flavouring. It's crafted to balance the juniper notes and refreshing taste of Gordons with lemons from sun-soaked Sicily. TASTING NOTES - Gordons Sicilian Lemon Distilled Gin's tasting notes include zesty Sicilian lemons balanced with Gordons original botanicals to deliver a crisp and refreshing taste. HOW TO ENJOY - Best served with premium tonic water and ice for a citrusy twist on a gin and tonic. It can also be used as the base of a gin cocktail for a variation on a classic. AWARDS - The Gordon's gin range includes multi-award winning spirits that are famous the world over for their unique taste, based on a blend of botanicals and handpicked juniper berries. PERFECT FOR GIFTING - Gordons Sicilian Lemon is a delicious and tasty gin - the perfect gift for gin enthusiasts. Gordons Sicilian Lemon Distilled Flavoured Gin gives a delicious Mediterranean twist to an original recipe from Alexander Gordon. Made with high quality ingredients and using only natural flavourings, Gordons Sicilian Lemon is crafted to balance the juniper notes and refreshing taste of Gordons with lemons from sun-soaked Sicily. Taste the Italian sunshine and take your taste buds on a trip to the sunny shores of Southern Europe with this flavoured gin. In 1769, Alexander Gordon started his distillery in London and set about creating the recipe for a brilliant tasting gin. To this day, Gordons Gin is distilled to the same exacting standard, and Gordons Sicilian Lemon is a delicious Mediterranean twist on an original recipe from Alexander Gordon.
Title: Gordon's Sicilian Lemon Distilled Flavoured Gin 37.5 Vol Bottle 70cl

TASTING NOTES - Guinness Draught 0.0 Non-Alcoholic Beer's tasting notes include the sweetness of malt, the bitterness of hops and the unique Guinness roasted barley. HOW TO ENJOY - Guinness Draught 0.0 Non-Alcoholic Beer is best served chilled and poured slowly into a glass. AWARDS - The Guinness brand won seven awards at the prestigious World Beer Awards in 2019 alone. LOVELY DAY FOR A GUINNESS: Perfect for summer, make yours an alcohol free one and enjoy Guinness in the sunshine. Guinness Draught 0.0 Non-Alcoholic Beer is a non-alcoholic beer with the same smooth taste, perfectly balanced flavour and unique dark colour of Guinness, without the alcohol. The brewing process starts just as it always has, but with Guinness 0.0 the alcohol is gently removed through a cold filtration method. This helps to preserve its natural flavour, ensuring that the all important sweetness of the malt, the bitterness of the hops and the unique Guinness roasted barley flavours are all perfectly balanced.

Description: ABOUT - Pimm's No.1 is a fruity and refreshing gin-based spirit made from a closely guarded recipe that infuses gin with a delicate combination of botanicals, caramelised orange and warm spices. TASTING NOTES - PIMM'S No.1 is a tasty spirit that delivers spicy herbal notes paired with the refreshing taste of citrus fruits. A fruity gin-based drink made from a secret recipe that infuses gin with a delicate combination of botanicals, caramelised orange and warm spices. HOW TO ENJOY - To enjoy a classic Pimms lemonade, fill a glass or a jug with lots of ice and mix 1 part Pimm's No.1 with 3 parts lemonade. Serve with strawberries, oranges, cucumber and mint. PERFECT FOR GIFTING - The ideal gift for those hosting a get-together, or those who want to celebrate a special occasion in style. GIFTING IDEA - Whether you're hosting a party, relaxing on the beach, or simply looking to unwind after a long day, Pimm's No.1 is the perfect accompaniment to any occasion. Savor the refreshing taste and fruity notes of Pimm's No.1 and create unforgettable moments with friends and family. It's the ultimate gift for those who appreciate the finer things in life and want to celebrate in style. The rich, reddish colour of PIMM'S No.1 Cup, with its subtle taste of spice and citrus, was brought to life in 1840. The secret recipe of gin, herbs, and liqueur was mixed by James Pimm in his London Oyster Bar to aid the digestion of oysters. It was not only sent to soldiers at the very edge of the Empire, but was also served at Queen Victoria's luncheons. Last but not least, the PIMM'S No. 1 Cup is known as the classic drink to accompany the famous Wimbledon tennis tournament and can still be found at many legendary cultural events. After all, PIMM'S is the signpost to summer! Pimms was born in London in 1840, when James Pimm blended his famous Pimm's No.1 Cup, a secret recipe of gin, herbs and liqueur - as an aid for digesting oysters in his London Oyster bar.
Title: Pimm's 1L

Description: Self Tan That's More Than Skin Deep Providing a tailored tanning experience for results that are as unique as you are, Technocolor Emerald Self Tanning Face Serum has been carefully curated through extensive skin analysis to deliver results that are perfectly matched to every skin tone, without compromising your skin barrier. Blending a fragrance free formula with the benefits of Dermachromatic Colour Technology, skin-centric active Vitamin C to help brighten, and Chamomile to help soothe, Technocolor Emerald Self Tanning Face Serum is perfect for medium skin tones looking to achieve a deep, olive toned face tan. Featuring mid-level tanning active ingredients, cool-toned bronzed colour enhancers and electrolyte hydration, Technocolor Emerald Face counteracts the development of orange tones to provide the most natural result. Additional Blemish Control Complex" prevents breakouts and blemishes from appearing, leaving you with an enhanced, skin-blurring finish after every application." Who is the product suitable for?"Why is Technocolor Emerald Best Suited For Medium Skin Tones? Technocolor was created through extensive research, specifically our laser skin analysis technology that examined varying skin tones and their ability to process self tanning actives which would determine their best outcome. From these findings, we discovered that those with medium skin tones were able to achieve their most optimal results through mid-level tanning actives, where anything higher would stress the skin and cause fading, patching or even lead to an orange tone. Technocolor Emerald Self Tanning Face Serum perfectly blends mid-level active ingredients, electrolyte hydration and Emerald colour enhancers to produce the most optimal results for those with a medium complexion. With every application, medium skin tones will experience increased tone longevity and natural results that best enhance skin, not change it. Want to learn more? Visit our Research Development page to learn more about this cutting- edge technology and take our Technocolor Shade Finder Quiz to find your perfect shade.

Description: PREMIUM BLEND - Savour the bittersweet Seville orange flavour, blended with iconic Tanqueray London Dry Gin, all perfectly mixed with premium tonic. MEDITERRANEAN SUNSHINE - Capture the essence of Mediterranean warmth and zest in every sip of Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla Gin Tonic. HASSLE-FREE INDULGENCE - Relish in the unmistakable quality of Tanqueray gin without the fuss of mixing, perfect for summer picnics or unwinding at home. AUTHENTIC TASTE - Enjoy the authentic GT experience with finely balanced botanicals and crisp tonic, simply serve chilled with an orange slice garnish. READY-TO-DRINK LUXURY - Experience Tanquerays quality in a convenient, ready-to-go can, ideal for on-the-move enjoyment or relaxed home sipping. LEGACY IN EVERY CAN - Tanquerays heritage since 1830 ensures a consistently delicious and quality gin tonic experience, anytime, anywhere. Indulge in the convenience and zest of Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla Gin Tonic, a premium ready-to-drink experience. Since 1830, Tanqueray has epitomised quality, and this offering continues the tradition, blending the bittersweet taste of Seville oranges with the iconic Tanqueray London Dry Gin, all perfectly mixed with premium tonic. This ready-to-go can is ideal for those wanting the unmistakable quality of Tanqueray gin without the hassle of mixing. Whether you're basking in the summer sun at a picnic or unwinding at home, Tanqueray Tonic cans provide a consistent and delicious experience for ultimate convenience. Savour the perfectly balanced botanicals and the unique bittersweet flavour of Seville oranges, combined with the refreshing tasting crispness of tonic. For an authentic GT experience, simply serve over ice and garnish with an orange slice. Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla Gin Tonic is the quintessential choice for on-the-go enjoyment or relaxed home entertaining, offering a taste of Mediterranean sunshine in every sip. Enjoy the legacy of Tanqueray, anytime, anywhere. Tanqueray distilling excellence since 1830. Tanqueray London Dry Gin was created by brand founder Charles Tanqueray in 1830 and it is still made to the same classic, timeless recipe today. Its iconic bottle shape is inspired by a three-part cocktail shaker made famous during Prohibition in the Roaring 1920s. The pineapple fruit was the ultimate symbol of hospitality in 1830s England and features in the Tanqueray family crest which adorns every bottle from the Tanqueray Distilling Company.
Title: Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla Gin and Tonic 250ml

Description: BANDOL Appellation d'origine contrle Naturoque Rose 2022 The Taste the Difference Discovery Collection showcases small parcels of wine such as this fresh and elegant ros from the Bandol region of Provence. This delicate, pale salmon pink wine captures the essence of Provence with its wild strawberry and vibrant redcurrant flavours. Fresh and elegant, the finish is long with a crisp minerality. Bandol enjoys an enviable location on Provence's coastline. Here the vines soak up the Mediterranean sunshine and enjoy the cooling sea breezes. The Moulin de la Roque winery grows the grapes for this wine organically with care and respect for the environment. Serve perfectly chilled with fresh seafood or delicately spiced dishes.
Title: Sainsburys Discovery Collection Bandol Rose, Taste the Difference 75cl
Sainsburys Discovery Collection Nerello Mascalese Sparkling, Taste the Difference 75cl

Description: Teroldego Rotaliano Denominazione di Origine Controllata The Taste the Difference Discovery Collection showcases small parcels of wine such as this rich, full-bodied red from the mountains of northern Italy. A rich, glossy and fruity red with intense aromas of raspberry and black cherry, followed by notes of forest fruits on the palate. This red is full-bodied and elegant with a luscious mouthfeel. Teroldego is an ancient dark-skinned grape variety from the mountainous Trentino-Alto Adige wine region of northern Italy. The vineyards are close to the Alps which create a unique climate of warm days and cool nights, perfect conditions for ripening grapes. A fantastic wine for meaty pasta dishes, rich stews or pork with crackling.
Title: Sainsburys Discovery Collection Teroldego, Taste the Difference 75cl

Description: Indication Gographique Protge VAL DE LOIRE BLANC 2023 Perfectly ripe, perfumed peach notes are overlaid with flavours of passionfruit and juicy grapefruit before finishing with a soft, peppery spice. This wine is made from Grolleau Gris, a rare grape variety which is almost completely limited to growing in the Loire Valley. The exceptional vineyard location and climate allow this aromatic variety to ripen to perfection, so creating a fruity and balanced wine with an alcohol level of just 8.5. This mid-strength wine offers a lighter experience with 64 calories and 1.1 units per 125ml glass. The crisp, aromatic nature of this wine makes it a great match for spicy food.

Description: Tasty responsible Great taste 2022 Gluten Free Our Proper Porkers... Made with the highest quality pork belly and shoulder, our Great Taste Award-winning sausages are bursting with bold, juicy flavours. Our Proper Porkers are beautifully balanced with a touch of sage and seasoning. Jolly Good Food for Jolly Good Times... The Jolly Hog is three brothers, all totally passionate about Jolly Good Food. What does that mean? It means food full of full-on flavour that you'll want to share. Food made in the right way, championing animal welfare and protecting our planet. Jolly Good Food for jolly good times - from our family to yours. Once upon a time, our lives were very different. A rugby player, a ship broker and a cabinet maker - three brothers united by a love of food, in search of the perfect sausage. 2007 - Given a sausage maker by his wife for his birthday, Olly makes our first ever sausage in his flat. Soon they're sizzling nicely and selling fast - starting in the carpark of Twickenham Stoop stadium. After several summers sharing jolly good times and selling jolly good sausages at festivals, we open our first restaurant. 2015 - Pigsty Boom! Our sausages hit the shops. Bacon quickly follows. 2020 - Lockdown. A bit of a gamechanger - restaurants and events go on the backburner, but our shop sales are heating up! 2022 - Our commitment to do business responsibly is recognised as we become a B Corp. We're jolly proud. What's next? Well, the future's looking tasty. Watch this space RSPCA Assured - Certification Mark, The Outdoor Bred pork in this product comes from producers inspected to RSPCA welfare standards by the RSPCA's independently certified farm assurance scheme. Certified B Corporation RSPCA Assured Union Flag

Discover our complete and balanced recipes with high quality animal protein and an irresistible taste locked in every bite to support a healthy, happy and active life for all dogs. This is why all of our recipes are made for your dog's needs to allow their unique personality to shine through. From our beginnings in 1946, Paul F. IAMS sought out new ways to create premium, quality pet food that would help give cats and dogs healthy, active and happy lives. Passionate about our furry friends, Paul believed the only way to provide the best possible food and pet care products was to understand cats and dogs better than anyone else in the industry. By spending time with breeders and nutritionists, he learned the importance of proteins and the role of fat in pet food diets. He was the first to consider cats and dogs primarily as carnivores, a perception which was to revolutionise the whole of the pet food industry. Taking in all that he learnt, Paul created his first small batch of dog food, Batch 999 in 1946, which he defined to be 99.9 close to perfection. It was everything he believed in and it set a new standard for pet food; advanced nutrition to make a substantive difference to the health and vitality of pets. This belief has become the basis for innovation after innovation. Today, we still believe we can enhance the lives of millions of pets around the world. IAMS is committed to innovation and quality by insisting on rigorous ingredient inspections throughout the manufacturing process, from initial truckload sample screenings to the moment our pet food bags leave the plant. We are not light when it also comes to control; with each batch of formula produced, we undertake a complete nutritional analysis to make sure all of our ingredients are safe for your pet's health and enjoyment. Through innovative research, breakthroughs and by following our unique nutritional philosophy, we're committed to give cats and dogs exactly what Paul IAMS intended; happy and active lives full of healthy vitality. With IAMS, we are here to champion the joy of healthy vitality. We provide complete and balanced nutrition that combines superior animal protein and an irresistible taste to support your pet's health without compromising on a tasty enjoyable meal. Giving your pets the tasty food they love, with all the nutrition they need from a trusted brand with over 70 years of experience in pet nutrition, no compromise. The joy of healthy vitality is not simply visible health or your pet's happiness; it is the powerful combination of the two together. With IAMS, you can really see and let your pet's true personality shine through. Nourishing healthy vitality of pets through expert nutrition they truly enjoy. No compromise.

Description: For Cats and Ferrets Spot-On Solution Prevents the Development of Flea Eggs Veterinary Medicinal UK Authorised Product Kills Fleas, Ticks Lice Kills biting lice on your cat. Indication(s) In cats: To be used against infestations with fleas, alone or in association with ticks andor biting lice. - Treatment of flea infestations (Ctenocephalides spp.). Insecticidal efficacy against new infestations with adult fleas persists for 4 weeks. Prevention of the multiplication of fleas by inhibiting the development of eggs (ovicidal activity), larvae and pupae (larvicidal activity) originating from eggs laid by adult fleas for six weeks after application. - Treatment of tick infestations (Ixodes ricinus, Dermacentor variabilis, Rhipicephalus sanguineus). The product has a persistent acaricidal efficacy for up to 2 weeks against ticks (based on experimental data). - Treatment of infestations with biting lice (Felicola subrostratus). In ferrets: To be used against infestations with fleas, alone or in association with ticks. - Treatment of flea infestations (Ctenocephalides spp.). Insecticidal efficacy against new infestations with adult fleas persists for 4 weeks. Prevention of the multiplication of fleas by inhibiting the development of eggs (ovicidal activity), larvae and pupae (larvicidal activity) originating from eggs laid by adult fleas. - Treatment of tick infestations (Ixodes ricinus). The product has a persistent acaricidal efficacy for 4 weeks against ticks (based on experimental data). Target Species: Cat, Ferret 1 pipette of 0.5 ml Fipronil 10 wv S-methoprene 12 wv Special Precautions for the Disposal of Unused Product or Waste Material Any unused veterinary medicinal product or waste materials derived from such veterinary medicinal product should be disposed of in accordance with local requirements. Fipronil and (S)-methoprene may adversely affect aquatic organisms. Do not contaminate ponds, waterways or ditches with the product or empty containers Pharmacodynamic properties Fipronil kills fleas within 24 hours and ticks and lice within 48 hours post-exposure. Description: Protect, Prevent, Clean For all sizes of pets Anti-Plaque Anti-Tartar Extra Cleaning Power The Beaphar Toothbrush, in combination with Beaphar Toothpaste, offers cost-effective, easy to use protection for your pet's teeth. Early plaque formation must be brushed away in order to prevent bad breath and tooth decay. This two-ended brush can be used for all sizes and breeds of cats and dogs. The handy soft grip makes sure the brush does not slip through your hands and it is specially designed to suit the shape of your pet's teeth. Different length bristles help you to reach all the teeth. Additionally, the bristles are soft and flexible for optimal gum protection. Why brush? Regular care of your pet's teeth will prevent problems developing, and reduce the need for expensive veterinary treatment. The main cause of dental problems is giving pets food that is meant for human consumption. These 'treats' often contain sugars that are harmful to pet's teeth. However, if you feed your pet on wet food, dental care is also important as this kind of food can stick to the teeth, and, without regular brushing, can cause problems.

Description: Kills Adult Fleas Within 24 Hours Stops Any Flea Eggs Laid from Hatching Prevents Fleas for 8 Weeks and Ticks for 4 Weeks The pet wellness experts Itch Flea 268 mg241.2 mg Spot-on Solution for Large Dogs Fipronil(S)-methoprene Fast-acting Itch Flea treatment is vet approved and scientifically proven to protect your pet and your home. The double action spot-on treatment kills adult fleas within 24 hours, halts all other flea life stages in their tracks and stops any new fleas joining the party. Plus it kills ticks and lice. Most flea treatments only kill the fleas, but our double action formula also attacks eggs and larvae too, breaking the flea life cycle and preventing any infestation on your pet and in your home. Because, seriously, who wants that? Fipronil kills live adult fleas, lice and ticks on contact. S-methoprene works by penetrating the shell of newly laid eggs or by being absorbed through the immature flea's body surface to prevent their growth and further development into adults, thereby limiting an ongoing infestation. (Sorry fleas!). Part the hair on the back of your pet's neck, snap the top of the pipette, and apply the entire pipette liquid to the exposed skin, then reward for good behaviour. It's as simple as that! Suitable for adult dogs and puppies 8 weeks or older. Not recommended to bath animals within 2 days after application of the product. This product can be used during pregnancy, consult with veterinary surgeon. Wash hands after use. Description: Proper food for dogs Expert dental care Developed with our vet dentist Chewy bubbly texture for a deep clean Made with natural ingredients Delicious recipe for happy chewing Vet approved recipe Woofbrush a day keeps the dog breath away No artificial colourings, flavourings or preservatives Woofbrush is the dental chew with a difference. Thanks to its chewy bubbly texture, the Woofbrush reaches the gumline to help fight plaque. It's delicious taste turns teeth cleaning into a joy! We believe all pets deserve proper food, and that's still true when it comes to dental chews. Because dogs eat their toothbrush and toothpaste' (their dental chew), it's important that their chew is as kind to their tummy as it is to their teeth. Woofbrush has been carefully crafted with help from our pet dental expert to make sure it works brilliantly, and uses top notch naturallike parsley, coconut oil and fennelfor a proper clean without the added nonsense. What's more, dogs absolutely adore the taste. From extensive feeding trials to the reactions of the office dogs whenever someone opens a packet, we know the Woofbrush is a chew that's a treat not a chore. We recommend brushing teeth daily but if this is not an option a Woofbrush a day is a good alternative and will help support your dog's dental health. This pack of 7 dental chews is just right for medium sized dogs to have one each day of the week. At Lily's Kitchen, we believe pets are family. Thats why our mission is to inspire pet parents everywhere to feed their furry family proper food. What exactly does that mean, you ask? It means mouth-watering recipes packed with natural ingredients and freshly prepared meat and offal. Its food you can trust, thats made to fuel cats and dogs and their daily mischief; ruling the roost and muddying up your freshly mopped floor (the usual). And as the first pet food maker to certify as a B Corp, we believe in using business as a force for good. Medium 11 - 25kg Certified B Corporation The Ethical Company Organisation - Ethical Award

When you hear them crunch through our kibble that has tailored levels of minerals in every bite, you can be rest assured that this will be keeping their teeth strong and healthy. The recipe supports healthy skin and shiny coat thanks to the effect of omega 3 and 6. Get prepared to watch them run and play thanks to an antioxidant blend of vitamin C and E to support their immune system and DHA to promote healthy vision and brain development. In order to give even tastier food to your puppy, fresh chicken is included in this recipes. Tailored protein levels are adapted to their needs to ensure improved digestibility of our products. IAMS supports your puppy's 7 signs of healthy vitality that you can see and enjoy every day. Nourishing your small and medium breed puppy's 7 signs of healthy vitality with 85 animal protein (out of total protein), all in a tasty enjoyable meal. Our dry dog food provides expert nutrition in a variety of flavours dogs like, to support 7 signs of healthy vitality all in a tasty enjoyable meal. Our puppy dry foods are 100 complete and balanced to support 7 signs of healthy vitality, for healthy growth and development, all in a tasty enjoyable meal. From our beginnings in 1946, Paul F. IAMS sought out new ways to create premium, quality pet food that would help give cats and dogs healthy, active and happy lives. Passionate about our furry friends, Paul believed the only way to provide the best possible food and pet care products was to understand cats and dogs better than anyone else in the industry. By spending time with breeders and nutritionists, he learned the importance of proteins and the role of fat in pet food diets. He was the first to consider cats and dogs primarily as carnivores, a perception which was to revolutionise the whole of the pet food industry. Taking in all that he learnt, Paul created his first small batch of dog food, Batch 999 in 1946, which he defined to be 99.9 close to perfection. It was everything he believed in and it set a new standard for pet food; advanced nutrition to make a substantive difference to the health and vitality of pets. This belief has become the basis for innovation after innovation. Today, we still believe we can enhance the lives of millions of pets around the world. IAMS is committed to innovation and quality by insisting on rigorous ingredient inspections throughout the manufacturing process, from initial truckload sample screenings to the moment our pet food bags leave the plant. We are not light when it also comes to control; with each batch of formula produced, we undertake a complete nutritional analysis to make sure all of our ingredients are safe for your pet's health and enjoyment. Through innovative research, breakthroughs and by following our unique nutritional philosophy, we're committed to give cats and dogs exactly what Paul IAMS intended; happy and active lives full of healthy vitality. With IAMS, we are here to champion the joy of healthy vitality. We provide complete and balanced nutrition that combines superior animal protein and an irresistible taste to support your pet's health without compromising on a tasty enjoyable meal. Giving your pets the tasty food they love, with all the nutrition they need from a trusted brand with over70 years of experience in pet nutrition, no compromise. The joy of healthy vitality is not simply visible health or your pet's happiness; it is the powerful combination of the two together. With IAMS, you can really see and let your pet's true personality shine through. IAMS offers expert nutrition in a wide range of tasty recipes for each and every pet, all to support your dog's healthy vitality. Discover our complete and balanced recipes with high quality animal protein and an irresistible taste locked in every bite to support a healthy, happy and active life for all dogs. This is why all of our recipes are made for your dog's needs to allow their unique personality to shine through. Nourishing healthy vitality of pets through expert nutrition they truly enjoy. No compromise.

Description: Delicious shredded texture Made with proper meat and fish Natural ingredients No added sugars Grain-free recipe Complete and Balanced Recipe Multipack 70g x 8 We've gone completely rogue (also known as 100 cat) and cooked up something that even the most independent feline will get off the sofa for. We're talking sumptuous shredded chicken nestled in a delicious broth, with a choice of additional mussels, ham, or our fish variety - Tuna with Salmon. Best of all, these recipes are made with natural ingredients, no added sugars (rare for cat food, we know) and of course, no grains. It's also complete, which means this food has everything your cat needs - no not all cat food does. But our cats inspire us to do great things on their behalf. Whiskered Einsteins. So make good choices (unless you aren't attached to that plant pot). At Lily's Kitchen we believe pets are family. That's why our mission is to inspire pet parents everywhere to feed their furry family proper food. What's proper food you ask? Delicious, complete recipes packed full of freshly prepared, nutritious natural ingredients. Proper food is food you can trust, labelled honestly, made by people who care. We think cats and dogs need proper food to live healthy, happy lives doing what they do best; ruling the roost and drooling on your freshly mopped floor. Lily's Kitchen is proud to be the first pet food maker to certify as a B Corp, using business as a force for good. Like Cats We Don't Take Things Lying Down (Oh, Okay Kitty You Do You) If your cats knows that your pot on the sofa is better suited to them, they'll go for it. Thought breakfast was best served at 9am? Kitty's here with a crack of dawn lesson or two. So when we learned that most cat food doesn't cut the mustard, we went full on cat and did the absurd - we made complete, natural recipes made with proper meat. Rogue, We Know, that's Just How We Roll (But Don't Touch Our Tummies) So cats, joins us in the rebellion. Raise a paw, twirl your tail and give us your best resting nap face (just the latter? Okay, don't worry, we've got you). All you really need to do is tuck in - see, told you it was good. All of this packed into a tasty recipe with 88 animal protein (out of total protein) for your pet to enjoy every day. - Supporting 7 signs of healthy vitality- IAMS for Vitality with ocean fish for adult cats is a 100 complete and balanced pet food that nourishes your cat's healthy vitality- Healthy urinary tract: Formulated to reduce urinary pH- Healthy skin coat: Omega 3 6 to support healthy skin and shiny coat- Strong muscles: High quality animal protein and essential minerals to help maintain strong muscles- Healthy teeth: Crunchy kibbles and tailored mineral levels to help reduce tartar build up for healthy teeth- Strong immune system: Antioxidant blend with vitamin E to help support the immune system- Healthy digestion: Tailored fibre blend including prebiotics and beet pulp for healthy digestion- Healthy heart: Taurine to nourish the heart- 88 animal protein (out of total protein)- No fillers, artificial colours, flavours or GMOs- Wheat free (produced in a factory that handles wheat) IAMS offers expert nutrition in a wide range of tasty recipes for each and every pet, all to support your cat's healthy vitality. Discover our complete and balanced recipes with high quality animal protein and an irresistible taste locked in every bite to support a healthy, happy and active life for all cats. This is why all of our recipes are made for your cat's needs to allow their unique personality to shine through. From our beginnings in 1946, Paul F. IAMS sought out new ways to create premium, quality pet food that would help give cats and dogs healthy, active and happy lives. Passionate about our furry friends, Paul believed the only way to provide the best possible food and pet care products was to understand cats and dogs better than anyone else in the industry. By spending time with breeders and nutritionists, he learned the importance of proteins and the role of fat in pet food diets. He was the first to consider cats and dogs primarily as carnivores, a perception which was to revolutionise the whole of the pet food industry. Taking in all that he learnt, Paul created his first small batch of dog food, Batch 999 in 1946, which he defined to be 99.9 close to perfection. It was everything he believed in and it set a new standard for pet food; advanced nutrition to make a substantive difference to the health and vitality of pets. This belief has become the basis for innovation after innovation. Today, we still believe we can enhance the lives of millions of pets around the world. IAMS is committed to innovation and quality by insisting on rigorous ingredient inspections throughout the manufacturing process, from initial truckload sample screenings to the moment our pet food bags leave the plant. We are not light when it also comes to control; with each batch of formula produced, we undertake a complete nutritional analysis to make sure all of our ingredients are safe for your pet's health and enjoyment. Through innovative research, breakthroughs and by following our unique nutritional philosophy, we're committed to give cats and dogs exactly what Paul IAMS intended; happy and active lives full of healthy vitality. With IAMS, we are here to champion the joy of healthy vitality. We provide complete and balanced nutrition that combines superior animal protein and an irresistible taste to support your pet's health without compromising on a tasty enjoyable meal. Giving your pets the tasty food they love, with all the nutrition they need from a trusted brand with over 70 years of experience in pet nutrition, no compromise. The joy of healthy vitality is not simply visible health or your pet's happiness; it is the powerful combination of the two together. With IAMS, you can really see and let your pet's true personality shine through.

Our senior cat dry food provides expert nutrition in a 100 complete and balanced recipe in a wide variety of tastes and textures to support your pet during their senior years. Our recipes contain all the essential nutrients, vitamins and minerals they need to ensure their digestive system is well looked after and we help them to maintain healthy joints for you to watch them leap and bound, all in a tasty enjoyable meal. Our senior dry cat foods are 100 complete and balanced to support the 7 signs of healthy vitality during their senior years all in a tasty enjoyable meal. IAMS offers expert nutrition in a wide range of tasty recipes for each and every pet, all to support your cat's healthy vitality. Discover our complete and balanced recipes with high quality animal protein and an irresistible taste locked in every bite to support a healthy, happy and active life for all cats. This is why all of our recipes are made for your cat's needs to allow their unique personality to shine through. From our beginnings in 1946, Paul F. IAMS sought out new ways to create premium, quality pet food that would help give cats and dogs healthy, active and happy lives. Passionate about our furry friends, Paul believed the only way to provide the best possible food and pet care products was to understand cats and dogs better than anyone else in the industry. By spending time with breeders and nutritionists, he learned the importance of proteins and the role of fat in pet food diets. He was the first to consider cats and dogs primarily as carnivores, a perception which was to revolutionise the whole of the pet food industry. Taking in all that he learnt, Paul created his first small batch of dog food, Batch 999 in 1946, which he defined to be 99.9 close to perfection. It was everything he believed in and it set a new standard for pet food; advanced nutrition to make a substantive difference to the health and vitality of pets. This belief has become the basis for innovation after innovation. Today, we still believe we can enhance the lives of millions of pets around the world. IAMS is committed to innovation and quality by insisting on rigorous ingredient inspections throughout the manufacturing process, from initial truckload sample screenings to the moment our pet food bags leave the plant. We are not light when it also comes to control; with each batch of formula produced, we undertake a complete nutritional analysis to make sure all of our ingredients are safe for your pet's health and enjoyment. Through innovative research, breakthroughs and by following our unique nutritional philosophy, we're committed to give cats and dogs exactly what Paul IAMS intended; happy and active lives full of healthy vitality. With IAMS, we are here to champion the joy of healthy vitality. We provide complete and balanced nutrition that combines superior animal protein and an irresistible taste to support your pet's health without compromising on a tasty enjoyable meal. Giving your pets the tasty food they love, with all the nutrition they need from a trusted brand with over 70 years of experience in pet nutrition, no compromise. The joy of healthy vitality is not simply visible health or your pet's happiness; it is the powerful combination of the two together. With IAMS, you can really see and let your pet's true personality shine through. Nourishing healthy vitality of pets through expert nutrition they truly enjoy. No compromise.
